<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <title>404 — Not Found</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Space+Mono&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root { --accent:#764976; --accent2:#5c5a9f; --muted:#7a6e99; --bg:#fafafa; }
    body { background:var(--bg); font-family:'Space Mono',monospace; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; min-height:100vh; text-align:center; color:#1e1030; }
    h1 { font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif; font-size:8rem; color:var(--accent); line-height:1; }
    p  { color:var(--muted); margin:1rem 0 2rem; font-size:0.8rem; }
    a  { color:var(--accent2); font-size:0.75rem; letter-spacing:2px; text-transform:uppercase; }
    a:hover { color:var(--accent); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div>
    <h1>404</h1>
    <p>Game not found. The code may be invalid or expired.</p>
    <a href="/games/word-search-battle">← Back to Word Search Battle</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
